Ti!

14
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:04,100
Noge.

15
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:27,200
Decko, ustani.

16
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:31,800
Sve je u redu.

17
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:44,200
Gde zivis?

18
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:56,100
Ovde je, bicu dobro, hvala.
